data.description: Stunning Kings Crossing Home! New flooring and fresh paint welcome you into the spacious floorplan, with tons of windows for abundant natural light! The large living room opens into the roomy kitchen and dining area, perfect for entertaining, with relaxing views of your backyard! The split-bedroom layout affords privacy to the downstairs Master Suite, complete with private fireplace for cozy mornings and a large en-suite Bathroom and walk-in closet. One secondary bedroom downstairs, as well as two bedrooms upstairs, ensures space for all to relax after a long day! Enjoy sunny afternoons from your large backyard, or escape the heat and entertain under the covered patio, with privacy fencing to ensure a peaceful retreat! Situated in the sought-after Kings Crossing subdivision, enjoy quick access to all that Corpus Christi has to offer, while still being just a short drive from the beaches of North Padre! Schedule a showing today!
